div(style="font-family:Arial;margin: 10px;padding:10px")
    div(style="width:400px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto")
      h1 Study Search Results
      h2 This is a Clinwiki Beta Subscribed Searches Update
      <p>Each search below is showing the count of any studies that are new or have any changed information in the last 7 days.</p>
      <p>The link is to the original saved search and will show the count for ALL studies in the search. If available in your site, you can set the "indexed at" date to a range to see the recently added/changed studies.</p>
      <p>To unsubscribe, visit your profile and delete the saved search. More functionality is coming soon. Email <a href="mailto:clinwiki@clinwiki.org">clinwiki@clinwiki.org</a> to provide feedback.</p>
      <br>
    div(style="width:80%;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto")    
    if  results.length != 0 
      each search in results
        p <a style="color:#0099ff;padding:10px;font-weight:bold;" href="#{search.savedSearch.url}">#{search.savedSearch.name_label}</a>  found #{search.total} new or updated studies
    else
      p No new or updated studies found.
